{"id":30023851058,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG_Y-cMg","head_branch":"fix-userrole-jsonpatch-lazy-members","head_sha":"975d100fb83a50a25faaefa23334a657162561ce","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":51350,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: avoid loading UserRole members during JSON Patch apply [DHIS2-21852]","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":81350109329,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAAS8NgokQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/30023851058","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/30023851058","pull_requests":[{"id":4078935473,"number":24489,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24489","head":{"ref":"fix-userrole-jsonpatch-lazy-members","sha":"03adef343f69fd5acc0b04f4ab45d8581a721c88","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"fc846bf0c2105183edb87a4b0b302e2aab06688c","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-07-23T16:09:22Z","updated_at":"2026-07-23T16:20:28Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-23T16:09:22Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/30023851058/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/30023851058/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/81350109329","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/30023851058/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/30023851058/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/30023851058/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"refactor: rework JsonPatch collection-exclusion filter to match FieldFilterService pattern [DHIS2-21852]\n\nAddresses review feedback on #24489 (Jan Bernitt): the per-call `.addMixIn(realClass, ...)` +\ninline mixin + filter-provider wiring in JsonPatchManager.apply() was rebuilt from scratch on every\ncall and didn't follow any existing convention. Reworks it to mirror the codebase's established\npattern for the same underlying problem -- skipping a getter during Jackson serialization based on\nper-call criteria, without invoking it -- already used for the `?fields=` GET path\n(org.hisp.dhis.fieldfiltering.FieldFilterService/FieldFilterMixin).\n\n- New `JsonPatchFilterMixin` (`@JsonFilter`) and `JsonPatchExcludedPropertyFilter`\n  (`SimpleBeanPropertyFilter`), shaped like `FieldFilterMixin`/`FieldFilterSimpleBeanPropertyFilter`.\n- `JsonPatchManager` caches one mixin-bound `ObjectMapper` copy per entity type\n  (`ConcurrentHashMap\u003cClass\u003c?\u003e, ObjectMapper\u003e`, built lazily via `computeIfAbsent`) instead of\n  rebuilding the mixin binding on every `apply()` call. `findExcludableNonOwnerCollections` (the\n  exclusion rule itself) is unchanged -- it was already schema-driven and generic.\n- The mixin is scoped per-`realClass`, not bound to `Object.class` globally: `FieldFilterMixin`'s own\n  filter is path-aware, so a global binding is safe for it, but `JsonPatchExcludedPropertyFilter`\n  matches by property name only. A global binding was tried first and found, in review, to silently\n  strip `Sharing.users`/`Sharing.userGroups` (present on every `IdentifiableObject`) whenever a\n  same-named top-level collection was excluded, e.g. on a scalar UserRole PATCH. Scoping per-class\n  makes that cross-type collision impossible. Regression test:\n  `testUserRoleSharingUsersSurviveScalarPatch`.\n- Answers Jan's second question (should an explicit patch to an excluded property throw?): no --\n  `findExcludableNonOwnerCollections` already un-excludes a property referenced by a patch path, so\n  it falls back to full (slower, correct) hydration rather than being silently dropped. Replaced the\n  previous `testUserRoleUsersPathPatchDoesNotThrow` (asserted only `assertNotNull`, would pass either\n  way) with `testUserRoleUsersPathPatchFallsBackToFullHydration`, which asserts\n  `Hibernate.isInitialized(...)` actually flips to `true`, mutation-tested against the fallback logic.\n\nNo functional change to PATCH behavior beyond fixing the Object.class regression introduced and\ncaught within this same review cycle (never released). All existing JsonPatchManagerTest coverage\n(14 tests) plus the new JsonPatchExcludedPropertyFilterTest (2 tests) pass; UserControllerTest (52\ntests, dhis-test-web-api) unaffected.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"975d100fb83a50a25faaefa23334a657162561ce","tree_id":"8269920bbd2c70438e6a320087985325d54cf330","timestamp":"2026-07-23T15:25:40Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscri